title: Akito -  Wonder Watch
description:
Alarm clock with a variety of functions
2 times alert
Displays the “ Krias shema” + “ Shkia”
Hebrew / foreign calendar
18 cities to choose a location for today’s times
Options for setting an alert before today’s times 2/5/10 minutes
Powerful vibration expansion
Shabbos mode – to lock the snooze button and ring the alarm for 10 seconds only
13 ringtones
5 ringtone intensities
3 vibration intensities
Rechargeable battery. When using the battery, turn off the economy screen display – to extend the battery life

title: Greentouch Model M3 - MP3 Player
description:
Greentouch M3 Player is the perfect combination between a compact and high-end music player. Whether you're on the go or relaxing at home, it allows you to play your favorite tracks with ease. With its custom UI and classic color scheme, it's one of the best looking devices on the market. And with a sleek design that fits seamlessly into your life, it's easy to see why this device is gaining popularity among music lovers everywhere.Features 

Music 
Voice Recorder 
Bluetooth 
eBook 
File Explorer 
Alarm Clock
Calendar
Yiddish language support 
NEW! English Yiddish support (it will read Yiddish from right to left when set on English)

Specs

32GB built-in memory 
Built-in speaker 

Bluetooth 5.0 (no file sharing and can not connect to a phone)
3.5mm Headphone Jack 
Micro SD Card Slot 
Touch Buttons 
USB Type C 
2.4" IPS Colored Screen 

Micro SD Slot (up to 64GB - Micro SD sold separately)
